description:
Find your personal favorite among the strong characters of the TanglePANDAs series C.
These TanglePANDAs are of the "hard kind" and don't tolerate any contradiction. 

Series C - Discount levels for members on the basic price: 50% - XP > 50 points, 70% - XP > 100 points (subject to change).
name: TanglePANDAs (Series C)
